this_title: The Jeff Lewis 5 Minute Comedy Hour Season 1
trans_title: Jeff Lewis5分钟喜剧时间 第一季
introduction: An online sketch comedy show. Each episode consists of one single sketch. All episodes are self-contained. These sketches were written by Jeff Lewis during his time with the ACME theater company. The show is directed by Sean Becker (The Guild, Awkward Pictures) and features guest appearances by Felicia Day, Vince Caso, Tara Caso, Brett Sheridan, Jamie Kaler, Kyle Bornheimer, Tom Konkle, Kim Evey and more. Written by Jeff Lewis
